1. Install requirements (Node, NPM, Yeoman, Gulp, Bower)
  1.1 NodeJS + NPM -> https://nodejs.org/en/download/
  1.2 Yeoman -> npm install -g yo
  1.3 Bower -> npm install -g bower
  1.4 Gulp -> npm install -g gulp
2. Use Yeoman Polymer generator -> https://github.com/yeoman/generator-polymer#readme
  2.1 npm install -g generator-polymer
  2.2 yo polymer
  2.3 Go get a coffee, npm installation is quite long
3. Let's try the app
  3.1 gulp serve
